  "commonIssues": "<div class=\"accordion\" id=\"issueAccordion\"> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading1\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse1\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>SAMPADA Portal Hurdles</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse1\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Limited daily tokens and booking issues on the portal.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Use the <a href=\"https://www.mpigr.gov.in/\" target=\"_blank\">SAMPADA Portal</a> to pre-register and secure a slot. Avoid peak hours.</li></ul></div></div></div> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading2\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse2\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Mutation Refusal & Civil Courts</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse2\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Revenue Authorities refusing mutation based solely on a Will if it's disputed.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>If disputed, beneficiaries must prove the Will in a Civil Court to obtain a declaration before mutation can proceed.</li></ul></div></div></div> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading3\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse3\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Suspicious Circumstances Claims</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse3\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Wills frequently challenged over shaky signatures or lack of testamentary capacity.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Include an MD/MBBS doctor's fitness certificate and ensure independent witnesses attest the document.</li></ul></div></div></div> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading4\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse4\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Property Description Errors</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse4\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Rejection due to missing Khasra numbers or exact boundaries.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Draft precisely using MP Revenue records to list all immovable property details.</li></ul></div></div></div> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading5\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse5\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Language Barrier</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse5\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Difficulties navigating Hindi-only documentation.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Engage a registered deed writer or advocate to assist with drafting and SAMPADA entry.</li></ul></div></div></div></div>"
}
